<Author>Kalina2
<Content>Conference type hotel Loved the rooms! Spacious, with big bedroom and a living room, (flat TVs in each of them), super clean and elegant marble bathroom. Bathroom goodies in a full set. It gives a full comfort and cozy atmosphere.Polite and professional staff. Only negative side is the location. The hotel is far from the metro station, although there are three Ms in the surrounding area. Each of them is far 10-15 minutes walk. Unless you have your lap top with you and use the hotel free wireless internet, the hotel charges its internet service 4 EUR for 1/2 hour. Also, we kindly asked the receptionist to confirm our stay in one of the Majorca hotels, where we were heading after, and they charged it. For a call of 1 min, it seemed a bit odd to us. They give reasonable rates for a 4* hotel. Pictures from the hotel posted on the websites are authentic to its original look. My husband and I both agreed that the hotel is a conference type hotel and intended for business people, rather than tourists coming for sightseeing. In any case, we totally enjoyed there, especially the first day when we did not even want to go out and meet the wonders of Barcelona! Kalina (Skopje, Macedonia) 
